.SH OPTIONS
.IX Header "OPTIONS"
.IP \fB\-l\fR 4
.IX Item "-l"
List configured directories. Boolean.
.Sp
Optional. Default: false.
.IP \fB\-e\fR 4
.IX Item "-e"
Edit configured directories. Boolean.
.Sp
Optional. Default: false.
.IP \fB\-h\fR 4
.IX Item "-h"
